## Capabilities

| Area | Details |
|------|---------|
| Logging | Structured JSON, correlation ID, trace ID, context logging |
| Metrics | Application, business, and custom Prometheus metrics |
| Tracing | Distributed spans + OpenTelemetry hook |
| Errors | Sentry-compatible capture buffer |
| Alerts | Severity-based alert events |

## Usage

```ts
import {
  registerObservability,
  observability,
  recordHttpRequest,
  prometheusText,
} from './src/observability/index.js';

await registerObservability();

observability.withRequestContext(() => {
  recordHttpRequest('/health', 200);
  const span = observability.tracer.startSpan('health.check');
  observability.tracer.endSpan(span);
});

console.log(prometheusText());
```

